  <h1 class="article-title">Get in touch</h1>

  <div class="article-body">
    <p>For corrections, tips, press inquiries, or anything else — reach us directly:</p>

    <p style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 22px; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="mailto:hello@rumormouth.com" style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--coral);">hello@rumormouth.com</a>
    </p>

    <p>A few things that help us respond faster:</p>
    <p><strong>Corrections:</strong> include a link to the specific page and what's wrong.<br>
    <strong>Tips:</strong> tell us what you know and how confident you are in it — we verify before publishing.<br>
    <strong>Press &amp; partnerships:</strong> include your outlet or company name and what you're proposing.</p>

    <p>See also our <a href="/about/">About</a> page for how we source and attribute content, and our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for how we handle data.</p>
